    Order Tracking Platform

    It is a platform that helps users to track their order/parcel online.

    Image Search Engine

    Web app to get different number of images for the searched word built using Reactjs. It is to view and search for different images using the Pixabay API.

    Conway's Game of Life

    The zero-player board game concerned with cellular automation built using the presented rules.
    A version of the traditional Conway's game of life built using Reactjs.

    Lyric Finder


    The solution to the 'earworm' condition to get rid of the song tune, that's stuck in your head when you only know a few of the lyrics.

    Polling App

    This is a voting quiz built using Django and Reactjs .
    View and Vote for different wuestion presented and login to create your own quiz.

    Random Text Generator

    Web App to generate random text for websites and sample web pages built using Reactjs.
    This is a online random text generator that can be used for sample web pages and design mockups.

    Web Scraper


    Tool built using Php and Php Simple HTML DOM Parser.
    It is used to extract data and different information from Stack Overflow website.

    Recipe Blog


    Who doesn't love food right!!.
    Page to view and add different recipes with user information built using Php with Mysql database.

    Article Blog

    Article Page made using Django with SQLite database.
    View and read different posted articles, login to the website and create your own pages and blogs.

    Typing Attack Game

    Typing attack is an educational game where user learns to type words quickly.
    Your mission is to type the words on balloons and destroy them before they reach the ground leading to game over.

    Snake game

    A fun game to play while waiting for things.
    Move the snake around with the arrow keys, eat the red dots to grow bigger, and avoid hitting your own tail.

    Ping-Pong

    Ping-Pong is built using Html5 canvas and Javascript.
    This game's goal is to hit the ping pong ball into opponent's goal makeing use of the keyboard arrow keys to control the paddles.

    Color-Walk

    Game built using HTML5 canvas with graphics drawn using Javascript.
    It is a game to select different color patches in the board presented in order to clear the board such as to get minimum score.
